title: GORGEOUS UNIT IN SLS BRICKELL!!
posting_body: ['Gorgeous 2 bedrooms / 2 bathrooms plus DEN apartment in Brickell.', 'Split floor plan on the 21st floor in the luxurious SLS Brickell Residences.', 'This unit features modern style floors throughout, high ceilings, custom made closets, blackouts in both bedrooms and roller shades in the living room, top of the line appliances, and a huge balcony with breathtaking views to the city and bay.', 'Enjoy 5-star resort amenities such as hotel room service, a rooftop, pool for residents , a pool on 9th floor, with a full bar and restaurant service, state-of-the-art fitness center, theater room, party rooms, lobby attended, security 24/7.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
